data.description: Welcome to 200 Ravenwood Court, a charming residence nestled in the heart of Bethlehem, GA. This very well maintained home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a thoughtfully designed open floor plan that effortlessly blends style and functionality. As you step inside, the warmth of the living spaces invites you to create lasting memories. The entire home is adorned with brand new vinyl siding, a testament to the owner's commitment to quality and aesthetics. The roof, a solid investment made 7 years ago, ensures peace of mind and durability for years to come. Imagine entertaining guests in your private backyard, an outdoor living space perfect for a fun dining or simply unwinding under the open sky. The new windows and back door, installed just 6 months ago, flood the interior with natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere throughout. Practical upgrades continue with a recently cleaned septic system, ensuring the home operates seamlessly. The front porch, repainted and repaired just a month ago, welcomes you with its refreshed charm. Indulge in the luxury of a custom closet in the master bedroom, providing both style and functionality to enhance your daily routine. Explore the possibilities that await at 200 Ravenwood Court, Schedule your visit today and discover the comfortable and peaceful living in Bethlehem, GA. Your dream home awaits!
